Loopback Policy:
Computer Configuration - Policies - Administrative Templates - System - Group Policy - Configuration - User Group Policy Loopback Processing mode

Terminal Profiles (Roaming):
Computer Configuration - Policies - Administrative Templates - Windows Components - RDS - RDSHost - Profiles - Set Path
Тут важно наследование прав Shared Folder, иначе работать не будет
Можно сделать по другому:
Computer Configuration - Policies - Administrative Templates - System - User Profiles - Set roaming profile path for all users logging onto this comp

Folder Redirection (отдельно по папкам):
User Configuration - Policies - Windows Settings - Folder redirection ; Properties - Advanced
